      mobile-broadband-provider-info</ulink> and
      <ulink url="http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/gnome/sources/ModemManager/">
      ModemManager</ulink> (0.7 and later)
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">User Notes:
